{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and we arrived in Jolsva, which is on the northern part of Hungary, at night, I remember.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they waited for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They kicked us out from the wagon-- we arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's where the military atmosphere-- a Jewish-labor-camp, military atmosphere started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't know at the time that, of course, this labor camp thing is our savior.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because those who, who, who stayed at home-- and I will give you an example for that-- have been deported with their parents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had one, one colleague there-- I'm sorry, I left out from the eight, one, one person, Spitzer Yuri-- because it was only seven-- who also perished.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was deported with the parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this Spitzer Yuri, he had a weak heart, right, was looking forward to, to, to-- not to be accepted in the-- in the-- in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he managed that with certificates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember the time after two, three days there, we had a, a physical examination.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was-- he was sent back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, that was a tremendous-- we thought-- a tremendous achievement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we sent messages through him back to, to Ujpest, by which time-- because the last few days have already started the, the movement there-- the movement to the new, allocated ghetto area.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I-- I left my parents in the old place there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have received letters from them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We send letters back to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother wrote mainly-- I mean, my mother was, you know, he-- he would-- she would never say anything which would sadden me, right?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So whatever she said was censored [CRYING] by, by herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
